TalonFXConfiguration (CTRE Phoenix Java 5.32.0-beta-1)

declaration: package: com.ctre.phoenix.motorcontrol.can, class: TalonFXConfiguration

Assuming this is the same/similar TalonFxConfiguration I don’t think CurrentLimits is a valid member of that class.

Look at statorCurrLimit, supplyCurrLimit

Either way… is it saying the fields aren’t valid?
